$date WaveCrux BLDC Stage demo $end
$version bldc stage fixture generator $end
$timescale 1us $end
$scope module bldc_demo $end
$var real 64 s speed $end
$var real 64 a phaseA $end
$var real 64 b phaseB $end
$var real 64 c phaseC $end
$var wire 1 m commutate $end
$var wire 1 f fault $end
